---
layout: layouts/base.njk
---
<div id="content-layout">
    <div class="vacancies__header">
        <h1>{{title}}</h1>
    </div>
    <hr>
    <div class="about__page">
      <div class="about__description">
        <h3>
          For 9 years we have been living web and mobile development: we design, test
          and implement. We make complex services enjoyable, accounting systems understandable, 
          and corporate systems soft and gentle. We say no to streaming development!

            <p>Now in the team: frontend and backend developers, QA engineers, projects, account managers, HR, PR.</p>

            <p>There are 50+ cool people in total ... But there should be more of them, so here you go :)</p>
        </h3>
        <img src="https://static.tildacdn.com/tild6665-6465-4438-a664-623633303466/nathanriley514162.jpg" class="about__page_img" />
      </div>
      

      <div class="about__users">
        {% for user in users | limit(3) %}
        <div class="about__user">
          <h3>{{ user.name | makeLowerCase }}</h3>
          <h5>{{ user.email }}</h5>
          <h5>{{ user.phone }}</h5>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>

      <div class="about__video">
        {% youtube "imOUKPruPHk" %}
      </div>
    </div>
</div>